1
00:00:01,754 --> 00:00:05,912
- Martial God Asura Season 2  -

2
00:00:07,682 --> 00:00:10,793
Episode 6
[Legendary Warriors Appear]
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

3
00:00:12,224 --> 00:00:14,224
[Location: Misty Forest of the Ten Thousand Demon Mountain]

4
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:21,999
What about the others?

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,439
They’ve all returned to the manor.

6
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,359
Just take care of yourself first.

7
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,320
What’s wrong with you?

8
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:32,159
This girl hasn’t slept a wink all night.

9
00:00:32,160 --> 00:00:34,279
She worked really hard to save you.

10
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:43,800
I’m fine.

11
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:45,159
I just need some rest.

12
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:46,160
Ziling...

13
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:47,480
I...

14
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,039
If you want to thank me,

15
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,320
then do me a favor.

16
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:54,959
It’s the treasure in Ten Thousand Demons Mountain, right?

17
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,079
I only want one martial technique.

18
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,239
You can have everything else.

19
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,839
Right now, Ten Thousand Demons Mountain is full of danger.

20
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,079
It’s clear someone is plotting in the shadows.

21
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,599
But that technique

22
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,679
is extremely important to me.

23
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,680
One extra person

24
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,679
means one more chance of seizing the divine weapon.

25
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,479
Fine. I’ll help you.

26
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,799
Are you sure there’s a secret treasure here?

27
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,120
No mistake.

28
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,079
On the map the Demon Monkey King gave us,

29
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,639
this spot was specially marked.

30
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,359
There must be something unusual about it.

31
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,640
It’s right here.

32
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,959
This statue feels strange.

33
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:58,960
Better not touch it carelessly.

34
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,879
My grandfather once told me

35
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,319
that my mother’s pipa playing

36
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:04,719
was unmatched in the world.

37
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,799
Ziling, this statue really shouldn’t—

38
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,400
A mechanism!

39
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:17,440
Oh no!

40
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,439
This is a realm spirit from the Immortal Spirit Realm.

41
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,440
Its strength is unfathomable.

42
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,999
Hahaha...

43
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,640
Hahaha...

44
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,759
This evil spirit’s aura is bizarre.

45
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,919
At least at the first level of Heavenly Martial.

46
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,920
We can’t fight it head-on.

47
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,079
We have to fight with our backs to the wall.

48
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,160
Find its weakness.

49
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,400
You okay?

50
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:52,559
Hahaha...

51
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,919
Why did she stop attacking?

52
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,519
She’s protecting the statue.

53
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,719
Looks like that’s the key to breaking this.

54
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,519
I’ll draw the evil spirit away.

55
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,159
You take the chance to destroy the statue.

56
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,239
Ziling, be careful!

57
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:26,959
Dandan,

58
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,160
lend me your power!

59
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,919
First, deal with that evil spirit.

60
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,560
Mm.

61
00:04:36,584 --> 00:05:05,084
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

62
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,240
Perfect timing.

63
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,560
Trying to run?

64
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,799
White Tiger Assault Art!

65
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,360
Ziling!

66
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:48,999
You...

67
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:52,399
Forget about me. Go, quick!

68
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:54,999
No. I still owe you my life.

69
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,279
I won’t abandon you.

70
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,879
It’s dangerous! Go!

71
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,799
If you want to take her life,

72
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,839
forget it!

73
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,080
Chu Feng...

74
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,839
Good thing it was just an illusion.

75
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,119
Otherwise, someone as foolish as you

76
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,799
wouldn’t have enough lives to spare.

77
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,119
I’m fine. Don’t worry.

78
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,399
A thousand years have passed in the blink of an eye.

79
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:35,679
Finally, someone has passed the trial.

80
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,639
This is...

81
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,079
the master of this place.

82
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:42,319
Young man, the path of martial cultivation is endless,

83
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:45,519
yet in this world, there is only one thing—

84
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,199
love—

85
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,039
that can defy fate

86
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,479
and triumph over heaven.

87
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,799
To save her,

88
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:56,079
you were willing to give your life.

89
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,919
That is true affection.

90
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:01,439
The martial technique I left here

91
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,279
is now yours.

92
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,199
Mm.

93
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,679
But you saved my life.

94
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,039
This technique should be...

95
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,640
We had a deal.

96
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,800
I never go back on my word.

97
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,319
Nine-stage martial technique: Phantom Sound Art.

98
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,159
It can disrupt a person’s mind

99
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,160
and even create illusions.

100
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,639
I’m afraid no one across the Nine Provinces has ever seen it.

101
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:49,519
This array is draining our spiritual energy.

102
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,399
Jie Yan, for your own selfish desires,

103
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,759
you charged in recklessly

104
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,239
without caring if we all die!

105
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,719
Sigh... forget it, forget it.

106
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,919
Let’s go.

107
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,399
That kid really stepped in dog shit luck.

108
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:39,840
We’re leaving.

109
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:43,199
Something feels off?

110
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,200
I was thinking...

111
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:47,679
How could those Demon Kings set up such a meticulous ambush in advance?

112
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:50,519
You’re suspecting there’s a spy inside the Supreme Manor?

113
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,159
The elite disciples from every sect

114
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:54,159
were nearly wiped out in Ten Thousand Demons Mountain.

115
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:55,359
Once you return to the manor,

116
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,360
you must be extra careful.

117
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:57,960
Then...

118
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,719
I’m going back to cultivate.

119
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,640
We’ll meet again.

120
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,839
Before I break through to the Heavenly Martial Realm,

121
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,280
you’d better not get into any trouble.

122
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,800
Mm.

123
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,040
Saving people comes first.

124
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,240
Brother Jiang.

125
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:33,640
Jiang Wushang.

126
00:15:33,664 --> 00:15:58,464
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

